{"tid":1435412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民間記者會，只須向公眾從申訴求，且不宜長期進行","createTime":"2019-08-09T04:51:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T07:36:50.000Z","uid":110123,"like":6,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3e334a65567a49c73244f6a029e60fd2c0135581","tid":1435412,"uid":110123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:51:54.000Z","msg":"民間記者會，只須向公眾從申訴求，且不宜長期進行<br />\n長此下去就會形成大台，萬劫不復<br />\n運動會轉向，力量就會分散，無力對抗極權<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wS0PDYcWh8U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwS0PDYcWh8U&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzQpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=178cec5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wS0PDYcWh8U</a>"},{"pid":"ed0a332c979b724e4a4e3898f60d6a30d69b05c3","tid":1435412,"uid":287173,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:55:18.000Z","msg":"始終係半個大台，不宜長搞，否則實有人搶咪號令天下！"},{"pid":"ee8542663f5ee00208103f43eff5c644d992fc70","tid":1435412,"uid":82082,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:58:12.000Z","msg":"一路我唔知民間記者會代表緊邊個民間"},{"pid":"9ad4ca0c40a067778c1dbe3b24b0b77819934644","tid":1435412,"uid":110123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:01:14.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"b2b929d896b50980d5dead213fe88c0bf3daa99c","tid":1435412,"uid":110123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:03:41.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"07f13ce60b0da248253086634a8f8c06d615fd0f","tid":1435412,"uid":4942,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:06:28.000Z","msg":"收皮啦又想老屈記者會=大台"},{"pid":"f20b395b39c919587e80908987a9cad92065a02a","tid":1435412,"uid":247798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:10:15.000Z","msg":"負皮，上一頁"},{"pid":"c69e9767a814c304e2d6a01403aa88f285b16b63","tid":1435412,"uid":212843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:16:45.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"6f56a001118e0abad0aaed2cc23948ab7a2577f3","tid":1435412,"uid":110123,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:23:34.000Z","msg":"連登一路做緊的都是左膠社運界慣常做的聯署、賣廣告、開記招。開記招的第一步唔係出採訪通知，係整一張傳媒聯絡名單，列哂每間傳媒機構收採訪通知的電郵、電話、傳真，無得玩即興，我100%肯定「民間記者會」背後係professional的左膠社運界搞campaign的老手，一路以來的全球買廣告位、聯絡都係呢類有興驗，做開社運、公關的才會那麼熟悉，與傳媒界關係好熟稔，這種publicity spin做得多唔代表做得好，但可以騎劫代言人位置，左膠社運界的文筆好屎，啱哂主流膠媒，大家一齊食屎。<br />\n採訪通知亦都唔會係素人抗爭者識寫的，可以google到格式，但你未浸過左膠社運界或傳媒呢行，係會覺得艱難的，採訪通知緊要過新聞稿，因為要吸引人來採訪。左膠社運界班人寫得多唔代表佢哋識寫，IQ低、語言能力差又自以為是，全部寫出來都係垃圾，我未見過但憑對左膠的了解估得到，正如鄺俊宇之流的文字會令人懷疑自己唔識中文，所以唔需要標青、食腦的人入行，全部業餘campaigner扮專業，包括Amnesty、綠色和平呢啲國際機構，上過佢哋網望過新聞稿嘅就清楚佢哋文筆好恐怖，讀咗開頭就讀唔到落去。<br />\n搞記招諗起頭都大，無街頭行動直接簡單，唔係素人抗爭者會諗到的回應，所以「民間記者會」班仆街一定係社運界出身，佢哋就係慣常把記招、廣告啲單調publicity spin當係抗爭，建立民間代言人地位。皇天擊殺連登，人血饅頭「民間記者會」，起大台搶代言人位置的冚家剷左膠，全部落地獄去見閻王，比地獄之火燒，永不超生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2407000772890915/posts/2423885587869100?s=1103535816&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2407000772890915%2Fposts%2F2423885587869100%3Fs%3D1103535816%26sfns%3Dmo&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzQpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=431d813b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2407000772890915/posts/2423885587869100?s=1103535816&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"d4399141d5293d7a0d48314618e1fb34679e58dd","tid":1435412,"uid":266844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:05:32.000Z","msg":"五大訴求要多方位重提，好多人理解唔深<br />\n<br />\n［民意戰］邊個唔記得五大訴求同我入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1435640\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1435640</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bdebeda7136537bbd94ba04450b1d697239cddd4","tid":1435412,"uid":274336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:10:41.000Z","msg":"睇嚟好驚民間記者會"},{"pid":"e0e635d368c17eb2e410f89fe4c88108a0b85bd0","tid":1435412,"uid":110123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:33:13.000Z","msg":"轉載<br />\n同道與民間記者會主持人的對話，歡迎大家自行去問他們fact check。<br />\n<br />\n不解釋，覺得不是大台的，你不再是我朋友，走！屌你老母走啦！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7sm0udX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7sm0udX.jpg&h=95201a1b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T5E9nyY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT5E9nyY.jpg&h=53efb2bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8afe3c47d9064ea591bc36badca2f697621a8fe","tid":1435412,"uid":36592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:34:15.000Z","msg":"分化post, 沉"},{"pid":"af17b40c9bed4924fd66790d70d0d866e84dbad0","tid":1435412,"uid":110123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b8afe3c47d9064ea591bc36badca2f697621a8fe","tid":1435412,"uid":36592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:34:15.000Z","msg":"分化post, 沉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:35:29.000Z","msg":"推，必須推倒記者會，盡一切手段"},{"pid":"971674c73620d994041ca724ca2c71555d18f5a4","tid":1435412,"uid":1581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:36:50.000Z","msg":"又大台<br />\n<br />\n呢排3毛好鐘意咩都話大台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}